<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NMT43">
<l>maṅkultōy ceṉṉi vaṭavēṅ kaṭattāṉai</l>
<l>kaṅkul pukuntārkaḷ kāppaṇivāṉ tiṅkaḷ</l>
<l>caṭaiyēṟa vaittāṉun tāmaraimē lāṉuṅ</l>
<l>kuṭaiyēṟat tāṅkuvittuk koṇṭu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>In order to perform the [evening] service for Him</l>
<l rend="indent">of Vēṅkaṭam in the North, whose peaks touch the clouds,</l>
<l>[Śiva] who put the moon up [his] matted locks and [Brahmā] upon the lotus</l>
<l>Entered [the temple] at night,</l>
<l>Having gathered everything [including] the umbrella.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
